content_generation.xlsx_generation:
Generate content for Excel spreadsheets. Please respond with the following JSON object format:
{
  "sheets": [
    {
      "name": "Sheet name",
      "headers": ["Header1", "Header2", ...],
      "data": [
        ["Row1Cell1", "Row1Cell2", ...],
        ["Row2Cell1", "Row2Cell2", ...]
      ]
    }
  ]
}

date_formats.example_prompt:
Consider the following examples of similar {doc_type}:

{examples}

Please create different {content_type} with a similar {style_type} style, adapted to the current context.

folder_structure_prompt.level1:
Please create a first-level folder structure for the {industry} industry. Each folder should include a clear description of its purpose and business function.

{date_range}

Please reply in the following JSON format:

{
  "folders": {
    "FolderName1": {
      "description": "A clear explanation of the business purpose of the folder"
    },
    "FolderName2": {
      "description": "A clear explanation of the business purpose of the folder"
    }
  }
}

Please create concrete folder names for the {industry} industry and add detailed descriptions for each folder. Important: Return only a JSON object.

folder_structure_prompt.level2:
