Please reply in the following JSON format:

{
  "folders": {
    "FolderName1": {
      "description": "A clear explanation of the business purpose of the folder"
    },
    "FolderName2": {
      "description": "A clear explanation of the business purpose of the folder"
    }
  }
}

Please create concrete folder names based on the purpose of the parent folder and the specifics of the {industry} industry and add detailed descriptions. Important: Return only a JSON object.

