folder_structure_prompt.level3_files_prompt:
First-level folder for the {industry} industry {role_text}: {l1_folder_name} - {l1_description}
Second-level folder: {l2_folder_name} - {l2_description}

This folder contains the following subfolders: {folder_structure}

Please create appropriate files directly for this second-level folder (not for the subfolders).

Please reply in the following JSON format:

{
  "files": [
    {
      "name": "FileName1.docx",
      "type": "docx",
      "description": "A clear explanation of the purpose of the file"
    },
    {
      "name": "FileName2.xlsx",
      "type": "xlsx",
      "description": "A clear explanation of the purpose of the file"
    }
  ]
}

Please create concrete file names based on the purpose of the parent folder and the specifics of the {industry} industry and add detailed descriptions. Important: Return only a JSON object.

