json_format_instructions.level1_folders_prompt:
Create a first-level folder structure for the {industry} industry {role_text}. Include for each folder a clear description of its purpose and business function.

{date_range}

Please reply in the following JSON format:

{
  "folders": {
    "FolderName1": {
      "description": "A clear explanation of the business purpose of the folder"
    },
    "FolderName2": {
      "description": "A clear explanation of the business purpose of the folder"
    },
    ...
  }
}

Create concrete and appropriate folder names for the {industry} industry. Provide detailed descriptions that explain the business purpose of each folder.

Important: Return only the JSON object. Do not include any additional text, explanations or comments before or after the JSON. Do not use phrases like "Here is the JSON" or "I hope this helps". Do not wrap the JSON in a code block.
